.TH "vmballoon_work" 9 "vmballoon_work" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmballoon_work \- periodic balloon worker for reset, inflation and deflation.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" vmballoon_work
.BI "(struct work_struct *work "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "work" 12
pointer to the \fIwork_struct\fP which is provided by the workqueue.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Resets the protocol if needed, gets the new size and adjusts balloon as
needed. Repeat in 1 sec.
